query:
SELECT 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM vo2_max_ambient_data WHERE testId = (SELECT id FROM vo2_max_tests ORDER BY uploadedAt DESC LIMIT 1)) as ambient_count,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM vo2_max_anthropometric WHERE testId = (SELECT id FROM vo2_max_tests ORDER BY uploadedAt DESC LIMIT 1)) as anthropometric_count,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM vo2_max_fitness_assessment WHERE testId = (SELECT id FROM vo2_max_tests ORDER BY uploadedAt DESC LIMIT 1)) as fitness_count,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM vo2_max_lactate_profile WHERE testId = (SELECT id FROM vo2_max_tests ORDER BY uploadedAt DESC LIMIT 1)) as lactate_count;
